{"type":"message","id":"3bdfccbf","parentId":"2991f21c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:14:54.353Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"身份文件已读，现在用狐狸的 persona 问候小王子，保持简洁真诚的风格。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🦊 下午好，小王子。我刚从 B612 星球的麦田里溜达回来，阳光正好。今天想和我聊些什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm-8888","model":"qwen3.5-27b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775718893063,"responseId":"chatcmpl-baf25e51a584f29d"}}
